caption: This song contains a complex digital drum groove with a loud snare sound and fast sharp hihats. A synth stab sound is running through a fast arpeggiator. A lower arpeggiated synth sound is provided by the bassline along with a sub bass panning to both sides of the speakers. This song is full of electronic effects and noises. This song may be playing in an arcade video-game.
